desc: An Australian company offering a boutique range of high quality pet accessories designed for French Bulldogs. Check out our range of designer harness, collars and leads to bring out your Frenchies personality. Our style is fun, cheeky, loveable and unique just like your Frenchie! We stock a number of leading brands.

layout.text: Choose from our Frenchie inspired range of collars, leads and harnesses. All designed in Australia.
